### ============================================================
### VERIFY FIXES — R2 File Storage & share_link Domain
### ============================================================
### File ini untuk memverifikasi bahwa kedua masalah sudah teratasi:
### 1. File upload tersimpan di Cloudflare R2 (persistent)
### 2. share_link menggunakan domain frontend yang benar
### ============================================================

### Ganti baseUrl ke URL production Render untuk test di server
@baseUrl = https://be-kompeta.onrender.com/api
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### ============================================================
### STEP 0: LOGIN (pilih salah satu sesuai kebutuhan)
### ============================================================

### Login sebagai Siswa
# @name loginSiswa
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "siswa",
  "nisn": "0001234567",
  "school_origin": "SMA Negeri 1 Bogor",
  "unique_code": "BUDI0001234X9YZ"
}

###

### Login sebagai Sekolah
# @name loginSekolah
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "sekolah",
  "email": "school.a@kompeta.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login sebagai Mitra Perusahaan
# @name loginMitraPerusahaan
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "mitra",
  "email": "mitra.company.a@kompeta.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### ============================================================
### FIX #2: VERIFIKASI share_link DOMAIN
### ============================================================
### Cek field "share_link" di response.
### EXPECTED: https://kompeta.vercel.app/explore/<slug>
### BUKAN:   http://localhost:3000,http://127.0.0.1:3000,...
### ============================================================

### 2a. Detail lowongan Explore (public, tanpa auth)
### Ganti slug sesuai data yang ada di database kamu
# @name verifyShareLinkExplore
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs/accounting-staff-1602be
Accept: application/json

###

### 2b. List lowongan Explore — cek apakah data ada
# @name exploreList
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?per_page=3
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### FIX #1: VERIFIKASI FILE UPLOAD KE R2
### ============================================================
### Upload foto profil siswa → cek URL di response.
### EXPECTED URL format: https://pub-xxxxx.r2.dev/profiles/students/photos/...
### BUKAN:               https://be-kompeta.onrender.com/storage/profiles/...
### ============================================================

### 1a. Upload foto profil siswa
# @name uploadPhotoSiswa
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----VerifyR2

------VerifyR2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo_profile"; filename="profile-picture.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample-files/profile-picture.png
------VerifyR2--

###

### 1b. GET profil siswa — cek photo_profile_url
### EXPECTED: URL mengandung "r2.dev" (Cloudflare R2)
# @name getProfileSiswa
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### 1c. Upload logo sekolah
# @name uploadLogoSekolah
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSekolah.response.body.$.data.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----VerifyR2School

------VerifyR2School
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="logo"; filename="logo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-files/logo.jpg
------VerifyR2School--

###

### 1d. GET profil sekolah — cek logo_url
# @name getProfileSekolah
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSekolah.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

